\par\pard\plain \tx0\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs26\b0\i0 Maggie believed Laura and continued packing up her books and folders for school. However, her mind couldn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t help but wonder. Sometimes it made her a little uncomfortable how fond Laura and Evan were of each other. If it weren\u8217\'92t for Evan\u8217\'92s affinity for PDA, Maggie wondered if a stranger would peg her or Laura as Evan\u8217\'92s girlfriend. Laura and Evan were playful together and enjoyed teasing each other. However, Maggie trusted them both and attributed their close friendship to similar personalities.}
